				{
					"type": "thinking_start"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "The user wants me to think carefully about style and then write a 300-word essay on agentic AI context management. Let me plan",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " this out mentally first, then write it.\n\nLet me think about:\n1. What \"",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "agentic AI context management\" means\n2. The key aspects worth covering\n3. Style considerations\n4. Structure",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "\n\nKey topics:\n- Context windows are finite resources",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "\n- Agentic AI systems (like coding agents) operate over",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " long sessions with many tool calls\n- Managing what's",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " in context vs. what's delegated/summarized is critical\n- Strategies:",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " delegation to sub-agents, summarization, selective retrieval, forgetting\n",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "\n\n- The tension between having enough context to",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " make good decisions and not overwhelming the model\n- How context management affects quality of output\n- This is an emerging engineering discipline\n\nI'm settling on a structure that opens with the core problem,",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " explores the key tradeoffs and strategies in the middle, and closes with why this matters.",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " I want to keep the prose clear and direct, grounded in concrete examples rather",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": " than abstract concepts, and maintain a technical but accessible tone without any unnecessary jargon or filler.",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_delta",
					"text": "",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "thinking_stop"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "**",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "Agentic AI Context Management**\n\nEvery AI agent operates within a finite context window — a hard",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " ceiling on how much information it can hold in working memory at once. For a chat",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "bot answering a single question, this constraint rarely matters. For",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " an agentic system performing multi-step tasks across large codebases, databases, or document collections",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ", it becomes the central engineering challenge. How an agent manages its context determines",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " whether it produces coherent, well-informed work or quietly loses",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " the thread.\n\nThe core tension is simple: agents need broad awareness to make good decisions, but they cannot hold",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " everything at once. A coding agent working on a feature might need to understand the project's architecture, the specific files",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " it's modifying, the test infrastructure, the user's intent, and the results of its",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " previous actions — all simultaneously. Naive approaches that dump everything into the prompt quickly",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " exhaust the window, leaving no room for reasoning about the actual",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " task.\n\nEffective context management employs several strategies in combination. Selective retrieval pulls in",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " only the information relevant to the current step, using search and targeted file reads rather",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " than wholesale ingestion. Delegation offloads independent subtasks to separate agent instances",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": ", each with their own focused context. Summarization compresses prior work into compact",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " representations that preserve essential decisions without retaining every detail. Structured task tracking",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " externalizes state into todo lists and plans, freeing the agent from",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " needing to remember procedural progress internally.\n\nThe tradeoffs are real. Aggressive compression",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " loses nuance. Over-delegation fragments understanding. Insufficient retrieval leads to decisions",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " made on incomplete information. The discipline lies in knowing what to hold close,",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " what to look up on demand, and what to let go entirely.\n\nAs agents take on increasingly",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " complex work — managing infrastructure, writing software across repositories, coordinating multi-phase",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " projects — context management will quietly become one of the most consequential problems in applied AI. The agents that handle",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " it well will be the ones worth trusting with real work.",
					"messageId": "msg_d2865652e001XuG2kHtbO0GuT5"
				},
